asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Hot Lips
description: At first sight, you can tell that this ex vet has been through it all.  Strategising major operations in the burrows during the wreck, Hot Lips is head of the FLUF Peace Keeping Force. Digging booby burrows like a maze for attackers to get lost in, and trenches to block would be apes and punks from infiltrating the underground, the old underground that is, back in the day, this wise peacemaker can outwit any genius with her cunning wit and mind. Like a top chess player she is thinking 10 moves ahead. Her camo fur helps her evade any enemy behind lines. The only thing apes and punks can see is a pair of juicy levitating red lips, which frankly they thought was a weird butterfly or some exotic slugs mating.  Then SNAP, they fell into her trap. When it comes to FLUF Space Force, I cant tell you, I am literally shaking! Now, dont let me forget. Comedy is her release. After hours, you will find her on stage in the underground Comedy Club, sipping on juice, nibbling on carrots and playing with your ears. Her quick witted, sarcastic and dry humour earned her the name Hot Lips for the saucy words that always leave her mouth.

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: The Zombie Queen
description: In life, she was previously known as Athena and was a successful AIFA referee, once officiating the FLUF World cup Final. She caught a rare strain of the FLUFID-19 virus which is believed to have been a byproduct of an experiment gone wrong in the darkest corners of the Underground, quickly turning her into the first red zombie.  She now stalks FLUF World looking to infect other FLUFs and in turn grow her Zombie Army. It is rumoured that she may be pregnant, which has sparked fears that a new breed of zombies is on their way...

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Ophelia
description:
O pale Ophelia! beautiful as snow!
Yes child, you died, carried off by a river!
- It was the winds descending from the great mountains of Norway
That spoke to you in low voices of better freedom.

It was a breath of wind, that, twisting your great hair,
Brought strange rumors to your dreaming mind;
It was your heart listening to the song of Nature
In the groans of the tree and the sighs of the nights;

It was the voice of mad seas, the great roar,
That shattered your child's heart, too human and too soft;
It was a handsome pale knight, a poor madman
Who one April morning sate mute at your knees!

Heaven! Love! Freedom! What a dream, oh poor crazed Girl!
You melted to him as snow does to a fire;
Your great visions strangled your words
- And fearful Infinity terrified your blue eye!
